abstract: Philadelphia Union beats New York Red Bulls, 2-0.
lead_paragraph: Vincent Nogueira and C. J. Sapong scored five minutes apart in the second half, leading the Philadelphia Union past the Red Bulls, who were shut out for the second straight game.

headline.main: Two Quick Goals Stun Red Bulls
